              "name": "Memgraph: in-memory-first, BSL 1.1 license (~$25k/yr commercial), reported stability issues"
            },
            {
              "name": "Kuzu: acquired by Apple, archived Oct 2025 \u2014 risky long-term bet despite community forks"
            },
            {
              "name": "NebulaGraph: little recent development activity"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Frameworks",
          "children": [
