            },
            {
              "name": "GraphRAG 1.0 (Dec 2024): 74x faster startup, 43% less storage"
            },
            {
              "name": "LightRAG (Oct 2024): ~10x fewer tokens than GraphRAG via dual-level retrieval"
            },
            {
